ŚThe Sorbus tree in the North side of the garden
was planted in memory of
Sir Terence Rattigan, CBE (1911-1977)
by David Suchet CBE
on 22nd May 2012"ø
śHAROLD ARTHUR DUDMAN:
MARCH 5TH 1923 - JUNE 6TH 2009
FREEMAN OF THE CITY OF LONDON,
WANDSMAN OF
ST. PAUL'S CATHEDRAL

[Second inscription added 2019]
ALSO HIS BELOVED WIFE
OF 58 YEARS
EDITH IRENE (LESLEY) DUDMAN
JANUARY 26TH 1926 - MARCH 24TH 2019
REUNITED FOR ETERNITY"ź
